Class FederatedStoreCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.cache.Cache<Pair<GraphSerialisable,FederatedAccess>>
      • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.federatedstore.FederatedStoreCache

  • public class FederatedStoreCache
extends Cache<Pair<GraphSerialisable,FederatedAccess>>
    Wrapper around the CacheServiceLoader to provide an interface for handling the Graphs within a FederatedStore.
